\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Your name and address?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Sinclair John Mouat.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 And the address?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Moss, Scousburgh, Shotland.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Are you married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Is your wife alive still?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 So you're a widower?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Which year were you married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 1926.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 And which year were you born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 The 13th of April 1894.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 That was here was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Not here, it was in a house up there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 But in Moss?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 In Moss, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 How many years did you live in the house where you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Seven, I should say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Where did you move then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Well - moved into a - one here at the end of this one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Do you remember why your family moved?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 
Well - they - they were - improved - improving on the houses, and old fashioned house they lived in. And they didn't have the room.- So they built a - house down here and moved here.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 It was a bigger and better house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Well it was - it was better house, yes, but not bigger.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 How long did you live in that one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Oh about twenty-five year I should say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 And then you moved here?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 How many brothers and sisters did you have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 I had one brother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 No sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Was he older or younger than you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Younger.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 How much younger?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Nine years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 How old was your father when you were born, do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Probably about - twenty-six.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Was he from Moss?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 He lived here all his life, he wasn't from further away?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 He lived all - all his life.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 What did he do?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 He was a crofter fisherman.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 He didn't have any other jobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 He didn't have any part time jobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 He wouldn't ever have been out of work as a crofter?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 How old was your mother when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 I should say twenty-two.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Was she from here as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 No, she was born on the - that place I showed you. Round there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 How far away is that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Oh - three miles I should think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Did she have any jobs before she was married to your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 She was - helping on the - she - left there when she was - but a year old and c
ame to another house over here, about - nearer the - close by the brew lock there. And she lived there 'til she married.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 And she didn't have any jobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Well she was - it was a croft she was on. And she was helping on the croft. She went - went to school from there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 She didn't go away in service or to work in a hotel or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 She was at service at a house over there by - you know, in Voe. Where you - not far from - where Robbie Bairnson is.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Who was she working for there then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Oh it was a doctor I think.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Did she have any jobs after she married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 No. She was - always at home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 How many rooms did you have in the house where you were born?
