\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Did you used to have baths in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Oh baths - oh we had a big - what do you call it - tin bath, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 How often would you have a bath then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Oh I suppose maybe - once a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Which room was the bath in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Well - it was the butt end I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 And she beds were in the ben end?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 How often would you have a clean set of clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Oh once a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Where did you eat your meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 In the kitchen. The - the living room like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Which is the butt end?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Yes, that's about right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 You always had your meals in there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Your mother cooked in that room too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 What did she cook with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 An open fire.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 And when did you get a stove of some kind?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Well we never got a stove any - up there - when we were living in that house, we - got a stove in this one - here.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Would that be before or after the war?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 That was - oh - I - it was after the war I think. The first war mind. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 When did you have breakfast, about what time? When did you get up as a rule?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Well - I should say about seven o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 And when would you have breakfast then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Well - would this be schooldays you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Oh about eight o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 And your parents and your brother all had breakfast together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 What did you usually have to eat and drink at breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Well - they had home - home baked bread. Milk. And - they had - their own meat - mutton or pork, butter. And - porridge.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Would you have tea for breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Oh yes, had tea, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 What about the midday meal, when would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 That would be about - one o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 What would you usually have for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Well usually fish or - potatoes and - or meat and potatoes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Any kind of pudding or sweet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Yes. Sometimes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 What would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Oh I just couldn't know - I couldn't - I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 What meals would you have in the evening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Oh we'd have the tea about - five o'clock.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 What would you have for tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Normal things, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 What was this at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Oh well - maybe tea, bread butter and egg.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Did you have any special meals or Sunday or any other occasions?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 No, I don't think so. There wasn't much change.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 You said your mother made the bread?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Did she make any other things like jam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Or pickles?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 She made jam in the summertime only when the - well rhubarb.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Did she make any things like medicines or bottle fruit, you didn't have fruit here do you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Oh no, no, no fruit here.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Did you brew any beer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Yes. Home brewed ale. That's in - that is from
 the - the bere, - bere, not the barley but bere. It's a - it's the same family I think as the barley but - bit different. The cars of the corn are different.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Who would do that then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 My grandfather. He got onto that - he - he dried it in a - a k
iln. And them he - he ground it on a quern, you know, a hand quern. Yes. But - that - is a lost secret now. Now to brew the ale from bere. Not barley, but bere.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 What else was there, it took some time to brew?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Yes, but I - I - couldn't give that - that's a lost secret, I just can't remember it.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Was it nice to drink?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Yes. It was very nice to drink.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 When did you drink it, did you have it with meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Well - yes, sometimes with meals and sometimes just for a drink.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 What did your parents grow in the way of vegetables and food?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Well - they had - potatoes and turnips, carrot. And - cabbages, yes. And rhubarb, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 What animals, livestock, did you have on the croft?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Well - they had about - six I should say cow and two horses and about maybe thirty sheep.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 And hens?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Hens, yes, they had about - over twenty hens and - maybe a - six or eight ducks.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Geese?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 No. No geese here.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 What was the size of the croft?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 The croft was - eleven acres of arable. And fifty of grazing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 How much rent did you have to pay for this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Six pounds three. A year.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 You had meat to eat every day really?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Yes. Well - yes, in season.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 When it wasn't the season you had fish or something?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 We had fish. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 You count fish as meat of some kind?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 That's right.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Do you remember getting extra meat as rabbits?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Yes, I got rabbits.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 There wasn't, much poaching round here?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 You mean poaching - rabbits? No, you could - you could take as many rabbits as you liked. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 What about salmon and that kind of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Well there are not many salmon here but you - you could - poach a few trout.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 That was counted as poaching?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Yes. It was, yes. But - these no trout here though - I mean, no salmon here I mean.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Do you remember ever seeing your mother have less food so that the family could have more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Did your father generally have more food than the others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 No, we balanced - eat his fill and that was all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Were you allowed to talk during meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Some were very strict and said children should be seen and not heard.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Oh no. That wasn't here.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Could you choose what you wanted to eat from what was cooked or did you have to eat a bit of everything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Choose whatever you like.
