\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 When you had a birthday would it be any different from any other day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 You didn't get any presents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 You didn't have a party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Can you remember doing anything special on Christmas Day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Well, we got a holiday from school, that's the only thing I know - special.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 You didn't have any special food?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 No. No, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 You didn't have any special events with other people in the neighbourhood?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 No, no. We got a holiday from school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Did you go to church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Church, no, not on Christmas Day. Except it was on a Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 So you didn't have the kind of Christmas we have nowadays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Oh no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Did you have any musical instruments in the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 What were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 We had a - an accordion. Have you ever seen one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 What did you mean by an accordion?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 I'll show you one. Do you want - want to see it now then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 You had an accordion?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 When did you get that's?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Oh well - I never got - I never had an accordion, I can't play any musical instrument.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Did your parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 No. My uncle could.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 He lived in the house further up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Did you sing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 No, I never could sing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 What about your parents or your brother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 So you wouldn't have ever made music together in the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Did your parents play any games with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 No games at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 No games at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Card games or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Were there any books in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 What sort of books?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Well - when I was going to school they had a library there, I got library books.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Would your parents have any books of their own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 No. We had a Bible and - but - and a hymn book. But that was all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Did they have any magazines or newspapers?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 They had - newspapers but - no magazines.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Do you ever remember your mother and father reading?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 What would they read?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Well they'd read the newspapers or a - Bible.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Did they read aloud to you or to each other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Oh no, they never read aloud.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Do you remember a funeral in the family before 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Can you tell me something about it, who went to it and what happened?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Well - the men went to it, not the women.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Didn't the women take any part in it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 No, no, never. They don't do yet.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Which men would go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Well every man who was physical fit to move.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 But not from the whole of Shetland but from what area?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Oh well from - the neighbourhood.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 So how many people went to the funeral that you mentioned?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 
Well that's near high difficult to tell, it depends on - used to go round the - inviting them, they didn't send by post they went - sent a man round by - to invite them, at the time and the place.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Can you remember any particular funerals in the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Wasn't there any way in which the women could show respect?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Well the women never left the house to go to the - to the church - to the cemetery.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 But the women were involved in some kind of ceremony when the body was put in the coffin weren't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Well you see different places and different ideas but I never saw that here. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Were you taken out visiting neighbours with your parents or did you go on your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 I went on my own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Did your parents take you shopping, to Lerwick say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 No. I was - I was - out of - finished with the school before I ever saw Lerwick. First time I went I was - I went by sea in a -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 What were the roads like then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Well not so good as they are now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Wasn't there any transport on land?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Well there was nothing on land - no transport except what was horsedrawn. Drawn by a horse or horses.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Would your mother ever go to Lerwick then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Occasionally. And sometimes they had to - they had - well they mostly had to walk.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 She'd have walked from here to Lerwick?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Yes. And except she went by sea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 If there was a boat going round she might get taken in it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 
Oh yes. If the boat from Sumburgh or Voe, she called at Voe at - you know, where Robbie Bairnson lives - and went - took in goods and - proceed on to Lerwick. Came back again to Voe.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 So this was a regular service?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 A regular service, yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Run by a person who made a business of is was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Well it was run by the - the Laird at Sumburgh.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 So he would run it as a business?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Yes, that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Did you ever go out just with your father? While you were still at school, did he ever take you fishing or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Oh yes, I was fishing, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Do you remember having outings on Bank Holidays, anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Never heard of them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 You didn't ever go away for a holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Could you tell me how you spent Saturdays in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Saturdays? Oh - well when I was old enough I had to work on Saturday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 What kind of work did you do then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Well anything on the croft, like we do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Can you try and remember what these were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Well I had to feed sheep. Mostly and - probably horses.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 The horses are the Shetland ponies?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Oh no, no, they're work horses.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Horses for ploughing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Horse - two horses for ploughing. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 You didn't have Shetland ponies then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 No, we never had - they never had Shetland ponies here - on this croft.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 The agriculture here is a big difference from further ...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Oh yes. Much - much different here.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 You've much more arable here?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 What about Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Well, we went Sunday school. And sometimes came back from Sunday came back from Sunday school and went to church at night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 So you might go to two ceremonies?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Yes. Two ceremonies, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Did you wear special clothes on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Oh yes. Wore - wore my Sunday suit.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 What did your parents think about what you should do on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Well I was never bothered with any work on Sunday, I had to go to the Sunday school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Your parents thought it was wrong to work on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 And your parents went to church as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 What denomination was this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Well - I went to Sunday school that was - well I - I - it must - the Sunday school I should say was - well a Protestant, but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Church of Scotland or United Free?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Well we had the Church of Scotland - Methodist, United Free and Baptists.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Which did you go to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 I went - to any one.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 You didn't go to the same one all the time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 And your parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Well they went to the - Baptist church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 How often would they go to church on Sunday, did they go every Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Once. Once - you see, there two services. One in the morning and one at - after - at night. Well they usually went - me mother used to
 go in the morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 And your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 He went at night sometimes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 He didn't always?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 He wasn't a regular attender, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Did you have things like Sunday school outings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Were there any social activities organised by the church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 One social - activity - in - might we had - we got the prizes. From the Sunday school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 This was once a year?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Once a year, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 What would happen then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Well we'd have the - something to eat and - a book as a present - a prize.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Who would come to this, your parents and everybody?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 No, no. Well, it was open to the public about - it was in - two men who were - were leading the Sunday school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Who should give out the prizes, anyone special.?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Oh one of them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 The laird wouldn't come or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Oh no, no. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Was there a choir in your church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Did you belong to it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 No, I never cold - I never could do anything on a choir.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Did your church run any temperance club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 No. Because there was no temperance club because there was no need for one, there were no pubs in the - in the place.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 But you had some home brewing you said?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 In many parts of England there was a tremendous amount of drunkenness at this time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 That's right. That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 But there wasn't so much in the Shetlands?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 There was none. Or I'm - almost none now. No. But - but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Even with all these sailors coming to Lerwick?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Oh well Lerwick there's been pubs in Lerwick from time immemorial.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 But round here there were no pubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Home whatever. There's never been - well - not quite I - not in my lifetime. Until it came - somewhere after the war. Hotel, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Was grace said at meals in your family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Were you taught to say prayers at night?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Did you ever have family prayers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Did your father take any interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Yes. He - he was a Liberal.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Why do you think he was a Liberal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 
Well - it's a long story maybe but - your first - politics who set the croft - the Shetland crofter free, Island of Arrens crofters free, was a man born in Liverpool by the same of W.E. Gladstone, the first Liberal M.P. and he set - gave them securit
y of tenure. So they were nearly all Liberals. In Shetland Islands. Because of - because he set them free.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Your mother would have had the same views would she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Was she interested in political at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Well you see, vote - women had no vote in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 But some took an interest all the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Oh - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Do you think your mother was interested?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Do you remember either of them voting in an election before 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Yes. A general election, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 He voted Liberal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Every time, yes. All hands here nearly voted Liberal. They nearly all voted Liberal.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Do you remember what elections were like in those days before the first war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 No, well you see. I had no vote in those days so I dint know anything about it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 You can't remember things happening now, you can't remember there being excitement and that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 No, no. No, absolutely none, there's no excitement, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 In some places at that time men felt they risked
 losing their job or their house if they voted differently from their employers, did you have anything like that around here?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Well that's what happened when the - the laird - before the - the - before - they were set free, by Gladstone. That did happ
en. But never in my time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 That act that Gladstone passed meant that the people didn't have to worry or fear the laird anyone?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Well never - they didn't - have to worry, so long as they paid their rent the laird couldn't put them out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Was your father a remember of a political party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 No, no, no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 Do you remember him doing any work for the election?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 So they didn't take any active part?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 No, didn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid331150 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 When your parents were not doing their work how did they spend their time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993156 SM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4938996\charrsid7932848 They were working all the time except when they slept.
